{
  "name": "MEHITS W3000 NX/LN non-Turbocor field view",
  "source": "Built from Modbus-RS485-registerlijst-MEHP-iB.pdf W3000 Modbus RTU table for non-Turbocor NX/LN style machines. Focuses on water temperatures, refrigerant pressures, compressor discharge temperatures, unit status, demand and alarms.",
