    "protocol": "Modbus RTU",
    "slaveId": 12,
    "baudRate": 9600,
    "serial": "8N2",
    "offset": 0,
    "notes": "Field screenshots matched 9600 baud, 8N2, Modbus RTU, offset 0. If errors appear, confirm slave ID, A/B polarity, stop bits, and slow polling to 2000-3000 ms."
